            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物关系",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4914,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/02/237301566/fa4c986eefe97522566b35be6e29e7a0_471244222089785302.png",
                      "name": "Элинас",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "所有美露莘的「父亲」。他曾经能够与女儿们进行沟通，但美露莘却再也没办法与「父亲」沟通，唯独玛梅赫还能听见「父亲」的声音。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "由于他非常喜爱他的女儿们，在他所创造的子空间内，化作了美露莘的模样。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4023,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/24/70239714/0513aa7f482dbb4778545d02f94956fe_5004007435087179259.png",
                      "name": "Нёвиллет",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "极力照顾美露莘的枫丹最高审判官。由他带领美露莘到枫丹廷，并协助她们融入社会。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4045,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/dd7d9c3c7e9285b9650a64fc6550622b_1437395977263774283.png",
                      "name": "Прорастающий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4043,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/1317767095153c379837899e6c332db7_7324951828922334601.png",
                      "name": "Камнедробящий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4044,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/622d9d846f1b800fa92b4c9c24ece5a7_2600000957143127249.png",
                      "name": "Большой прорастающий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4042,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/20/70239714/d94d8c4feac0e0795a26552689d6689c_2170865110424809568.png",
                      "name": "Большой камнедробящий протоген расщелин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "由厄里那斯创造的生命体，其目的是为了保护他的女儿们。",
                      "type": "text"
